{"tid":1907602,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多個素人區議員裡面，除咗睇靚女，呢個都幾值得留意","createTime":"2020-03-02T17:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T07:24:00.000Z","uid":63364,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1a2df2f7022d58ea5d63517443cc41d24cce1e29","tid":1907602,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T17:08:05.000Z","msg":"有好多素人選到之後，做嘅野同傳統泛民建制區議員冇乜分别，只系冠上咗素人兩隻字，但呢個就唔同<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n講過會有黃絲專屬口罩，<br />\n我地突襲多間黃店~<br />\n派。<br />\n口。<br />\n罩！！！<br />\n<br />\n有人話「黃藍是政見，黑白是良知」，派口罩予老弱是良知問題；而我話黃藍根本就係良知問題。有商戶搵我地合作無差別派口罩，我地寧願推咗佢；我地有問過認識嘅黃絲街坊戰友需唔需要預留口罩，但好多都叫我地留俾有需要嘅人。收到有心人捐口罩，唔想只做蛇齋餅糭，點先可以承載多一重意義？<br />\n<br />\n直到有街坊拎住一批貼好文宣嘅口罩送俾我地。<br />\n我地問：不如咁樣派好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n一班街坊、義工，戴埋頭盔、口罩、豬咀，行勻旺角十幾間黃到金嘅餐廳，逐間入去，《榮光》響起，將口罩逐枱派俾食客。喺咁艱難嘅時候仍然支持黃色經濟圈，你地係值得鼓勵嘅！疫症之下，唔少黃店都大嘆艱苦經營，希望都可以幫到鋪頭打打氣。<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，餐廳入面嘅黃朋友都好好心地，叫我地留俾有需要嘅人。但呢一包口罩，係俾支持運動嘅香港人相認；當你將口罩轉贈俾身邊有需要人士，同樣可以將運動嘅訊息散播開去。<br />\n<br />\n太子 8.31 六個月紀念，再有 115 位手足被捕。希望收到口罩嘅朋友，在抗疫同時毋忘整場運動嘅精神、同路人嘅付出，<br />\n我地。<br />\n一。<br />\n齊。<br />\n行。<br />\n落。<br />\n去！！！<br />\n直到煲底相見！！！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n重組警隊，刻不容緩！<br />\n<br />\n蕭朱辦仲有旺角南朱江瑋一齊派 ;)<br />\n<br />\n鳴謝黃到金嘅餐廳：<br />\nUnder Vacuum - 慢煮工業  青花亭<br />\n#基隆茶餐廳  Fong Waa Parlour 芳華絕代<br />\n桔梗 <a href=\"http://JIEGENGE.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FJIEGENGE.HK&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=18356595\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">JIEGENGE.HK</a>  辛安東元祖奶奶雞<br />\nJoyful Dessert House  火鍋撚 Hot Pot Land<br />\n申子居酒屋 Shinko  獨 ‧ 火鍋撚 Lonely Hot Pot Land<br />\n#一生懸麵  深宵食堂-旺角店<br />\n日常料理 Mainichi  WOFT  八福<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n【旺角北。蕭德健辦事處】<br />\n<br />\n2768 9355 / 9755 2205<br />\n亞皆老街 39-41 號金山商業大廈 7 樓 A 室<br />\ntksiu2019@gmail.com<br />\nTelegram <a href=\"https://t.me/mknonfire\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmknonfire&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=95e099e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/mknonfire</a><br />\n<br />\n#蕭朱辦 #光復香港 #時代革命<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JN78KSf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJN78KSf.jpg&h=484259a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/116017689789351/posts/215695093154943/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F116017689789351%2Fposts%2F215695093154943%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=6105cf88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/116017689789351/posts/215695093154943/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"e5b9fe752c639a9b35a81d2921c2d07650c9130c","tid":1907602,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T17:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e085823cdf6e63c6a5eeb2737d5c01e267692f","tid":1907602,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T17:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5ae87a51992fc2112d2b841e3e3c3f7bff3d4f","tid":1907602,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c75751d07e8dd771e426d938d0e5fbd9434ae3","tid":1907602,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T17:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41a4340ba99d3858dd324931598863e9841b4b4","tid":1907602,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T17:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7f0eb826854907696b4089db47410dc7131faa","tid":1907602,"uid":63364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T17:19:16.000Z","msg":"<